original_title: SKE48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト50 2012
overview: The SKE48 Request Hour Setlist Best 50 2012 was held from October 11 to October 12, 2012 at Zepp Nagoya. Fans voted for their favorite SKE48 singles/albums/stage songs. The DVD of the concert was released on March 9th, 2013.
title: SKE48 Request Hour Setlist Best 50 2012
